H. No. 3569 / 57 OG No. 9, 1558 (February 27, 1961)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 2835, June 19, 1960 ]

AN ACT CREATING CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF MIDSAYAP, PROVINCE OF COTABATO.

Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Midsayap, Province of Cotabato, are converted into barrios therein, to wit:

Sitio Dado to Barrio Dado;

Sitio Central Bulanan (Km. 52) to Barrio Central Bulanan (Km. 52);

Sitio Malamote to Barrio Malamote;

Sitio Samlang to Barrio Samlang;

Sitio Kiloyno to Barrio Kiloyno;

Sitio Biacnabato to Barrio Biacnabato;

Sitio Kamanal to Barrio Kamanal; and

Sitio Pacao to Barrio Pacao.

SEC 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted without Executive approval, June 19, 1960.
